      <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-navy mb-4">FDA &amp; 3A Compliance</h2>
      <p class="text-text-light mb-4">
        For food and beverage applications, Dolphin Centrifuge supplies systems built to FDA and 3A sanitary standards. This includes 316L stainless steel wetted surfaces, sanitary tri-clamp connections, electropolished bowl interiors (Ra &le; 32 &micro;in), and food-grade gaskets and seals. All materials are fully traceable with mill certificates available on request.
      </p>
      <p class="text-text-light mb-8">
        Common food-grade centrifuge applications include <a href="/beer-wine-centrifuge/" class="text-navy font-semibold hover:text-gold transition-colors">beer and wine clarification</a>, <a href="/food-grade-centrifuge/" class="text-navy font-semibold hover:text-gold transition-colors">edible oil polishing</a>, juice clarification, dairy processing, and <a href="/fish-processing-centrifuge/" class="text-navy font-semibold hover:text-gold transition-colors">fish oil separation</a>.
