        <li>&#8226; <a href="/beer-wine-centrifuge/" class="text-navy font-semibold hover:text-gold transition-colors">Beer and wine clarification</a> &mdash; yeast removal, cold stabilization</li>
        <li>&#8226; <a href="/machine-coolant-centrifuge/" class="text-navy font-semibold hover:text-gold transition-colors">Machining coolant recovery</a> &mdash; tramp oil and fines removal</li>
        <li>&#8226; <a href="/wastewater-centrifuge/" class="text-navy font-semibold hover:text-gold transition-colors">Wastewater treatment</a> &mdash; oily water separation, sludge removal</li>
        <li>&#8226; <a href="/algae-centrifuge/" class="text-navy font-semibold hover:text-gold transition-colors">Algae harvesting</a> &mdash; biomass concentration and dewatering</li>
        <li>&#8226; Pharmaceutical clarification &mdash; cell debris removal, protein recovery</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-navy mb-4">Related Resources</h2>
